      "writtenOn": "2019-02-15T19:16:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I wonder if it\u0027d be better to just choose to make the pentagon one triangle and one quad by splitting using the line from the quad corner \"opposite\" the intersection points to one of the intersection points. It\u0027d avoid the T-junctions.",
